name: LabQuest Document
summary: Learn about .QMBL files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: You can save QMBL files to the storages space on the LabQuest device or exported to external storage space such as a microSD card or USB flash drive. The file can also be opened by Vernier's Logger Pro and Logger Lite applications. While the Graphical Analysis iOS app can import most data from the QMBL file, it cannot import calculated columns from the file.

description: Data file created and used by LabQuest, an interface used to collect sensor data; stores experiment results recorded from a LabQuest device; may contain data-collection settings, data tables, analyses, graphs, and notes.
